import React from 'react';
import {FooterContainer, FooterWrap, SocialMedia, SocialMediaWrap, SocialLogo, SocialIcons, SocialIconLink } from './FooterElements';

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <FooterContainer>
      <FooterWrap>
          <SocialMedia>
              <SocialMediaWrap>
                <SocialLogo to="/">Pizza</SocialLogo>
                <SocialIcons>
                  {/*-------- Facebook -------- */}
                  <SocialIconLink href="/" to="_blanck" arial-label="Facebook" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <FaFacebook />
                  </SocialIconLink>
                  {/*-------- Facebook -------- */}
                  <SocialIconLink href="/" to="_blanck" arial-label="Facebook" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <FaFacebook />
                  </SocialIconLink>
                  {/*-------- Facebook -------- */}
                  <SocialIconLink href="/" to="_blanck" arial-label="Facebook" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <FaFacebook />
                  </SocialIconLink>
                  {/*-------- Facebook -------- */}
                  <SocialIconLink href="/" to="_blanck" arial-label="Facebook" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <FaFacebook />
                  </SocialIconLink>
                </SocialIcons>
              </SocialMediaWrap>
          </SocialMedia>
      </FooterWrap>
    </FooterContainer>
  )
}

export default Footer
